## SECTION B ‚Äî Invoice Ninja Setup

Open https://invoice.photobooth.local ‚Üí Follow the setup wizard.

### Products to Create
Navigate: **Settings ‚Üí Products**

Create these 9 products (all with tax enabled):

| Product Name | Price | Description |
|-------------|-------|-------------|
| Photo Booth ‚Äî Standard Package | 59900 | 3-hour booth, unlimited prints, props |
| Photo Booth ‚Äî Premium Package | 89900 | 4-hour booth, custom backdrop, green screen |
| Photo Booth ‚Äî Deluxe Package | 129900 | 5-hour booth, all premium features + social sharing |
| Additional Hour | 15000 | Per hour beyond package |
| Custom Backdrop | 7500 | Themed backdrop design & print |
| Green Screen Experience | 10000 | Digital background replacement |
| Photo Album | 4500 | Physical album with event photos |
| USB Drive | 2500 | Digital copies on branded USB |
| Travel Fee | 0 | Calculated per event (override in quote) |

### Expense Categories
Navigate: **Settings ‚Üí Expense Categories**

Create these 10 categories:
1. Ink & Paper
2. Props & Costumes
3. Vehicle Fuel
4. Vehicle Maintenance
5. Equipment Repair
6. Software Subscriptions
7. Marketing & Ads
8. Insurance
9. Venue Parking
10. Meals & Per Diem

### Tax Rate
Navigate: **Settings ‚Üí Tax Rates**
- Add your state's sales tax rate (e.g., OH = 5.75%)

### API Token
Navigate: **Settings ‚Üí Account Management ‚Üí API Tokens**
- Click **New Token**, name it "Dashboard"
- Copy token ‚Üí paste into `dashboard/js/config.js` as `INVOICE_NINJA_API_TOKEN`

### Company Settings
Navigate: **Settings ‚Üí Company Details**
- Upload your business logo
- Fill business name, address, phone, email

